---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Hero from '../components/Hero.astro';
import ContactForm from '../components/ContactForm.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Contact Us" 
  description="Get in touch with Virgen de Loreto Nursery School. Contact information, enrollment inquiries, and visit scheduling."
>
  <Hero 
    title="Contact Us"
    subtitle="We're here to answer your questions and help your family join our community"
    image="https://images.pexels.com/photos/207691/pexels-photo-207691.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=2"
    imageAlt="School building with colorful exterior"
    height="medium"
  />

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- Contact Information -->
        <div>
          <div class="section-heading text-left">
            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-lg mb-8">
            We'd love to hear from you! Whether you're interested in enrolling your child, scheduling a visit, or simply have questions about our programs, our team is here to help.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-6 mb-8">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Address</h3>
                <p>Calle Principal 123<br>Madrid, Spain 28001</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Phone</h3>
                <p>+34 912 345 678</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Email</h3>
                <p>info@virgendloreto.edu</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-primary-100 flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Office Hours</h3>
                <p>Monday - Friday: 8:00 AM - 6:00 PM<br>Saturday: 9:00 AM - 1:00 PM (By appointment)<br>Sunday: Closed</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="paper-bg p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">School Year 2025-2026</h3>
            <p class="mb-4">Enrollment for the upcoming school year is now open. Space is limited, so we encourage interested families to contact us soon.</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-accent-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Fall Term: September 2 - December 20, 2025</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-accent-500 mr-2 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                </svg>
                <span>Spring Term: January 7 - June 19, 2026</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Contact Form -->
        <div>
          <ContactForm />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Map Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-primary-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>Find Us</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="paper-bg p-4 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <!-- Map placeholder (in a real project, this would be replaced with an actual map) -->
        <div class="h-96 bg-gray-200 rounded flex items-center justify-center">
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-center p-8">
            This is where an interactive map would be displayed.<br>
            In a full implementation, this would be integrated with Google Maps or another mapping service.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-lg mb-4">
          Conveniently located in central Madrid, our school is easily accessible by public transportation.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
          <div class="bg-white py-2 px-4 rounded-full flex items-center shadow-sm">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-primary-600 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 5l7 7-7 7M5 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
            <span>Metro Line 2: Station Name</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white py-2 px-4 rounded-full flex items-center shadow-sm">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-secondary-600 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path d="M9 17a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM19 17a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16V6a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a1 1 0 00-1 1v10a1 1 0 001 1h1m8-1a1 1 0 01-1 1H9m4-1V8a1 1 0 011-1h2.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l3.414 3.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V16a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1m-6-1a1 1 0 001 1h1M5 17a2 2 0 104 0m-4 0a2 2 0 114 0m6 0a2 2 0 104 0m-4 0a2 2 0 114 0" />
            </svg>
            <span>Bus Routes: 14, 27, 45</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white py-2 px-4 rounded-full flex items-center shadow-sm">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5 text-accent-600 mr-2" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 8h14M5 8a2 2 0 110-4h14a2 2 0 110 4M5 8v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V8m-9 4h4" />
            </svg>
            <span>Parking Available Nearby</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="paper-bg rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer p-4 bg-primary-50">
                <span>What are your hours of operation?</span>
                <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                  <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24">
                    <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                  </svg>
                </span>
              </summary>
              <div class="p-4 border-t border-gray-100">
                <p>Our standard hours are Monday through Friday from 8:00 AM to 6:00 PM. We offer flexible scheduling options including half-day programs, full-day programs, and extended care.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
          </div>
          
          <div class="paper-bg rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer p-4 bg-primary-50">
                <span>What ages do you accept?</span>
                <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                  <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24">
                    <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                  </svg>
                </span>
              </summary>
              <div class="p-4 border-t border-gray-100">
                <p>We provide care and education for children from 6 months to 6 years of age. Our programs are divided by age groups to ensure developmentally appropriate activities and environments.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
          </div>
          
          <div class="paper-bg rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer p-4 bg-primary-50">
                <span>What is the enrollment process?</span>
                <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                  <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24">
                    <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                  </svg>
                </span>
              </summary>
              <div class="p-4 border-t border-gray-100">
                <p>The enrollment process begins with a school tour and meeting with our director. After the visit, families can submit an application. Once accepted, we provide an enrollment packet with all necessary forms and information to complete the registration process.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
          </div>
          
          <div class="paper-bg rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer p-4 bg-primary-50">
                <span>Do you provide meals?</span>
                <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                  <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24">
                    <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                  </svg>
                </span>
              </summary>
              <div class="p-4 border-t border-gray-100">
                <p>Yes, we provide nutritious morning and afternoon snacks. For lunch, families can choose our meal program or send a packed lunch from home. All meals meet nutritional guidelines and we accommodate dietary restrictions and allergies.</p>
              </div>
            </details>
          </div>
          
          <div class="paper-bg rounded-lg shadow-sm overflow-hidden">
            <details class="group">
              <summary class="flex justify-between items-center font-medium cursor-pointer p-4 bg-primary-50">
                <span>What is your teacher-to-child ratio?</span>
                <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
                  <svg fill="none" height="24" shape-rendering="geometricPrecision" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="24">
                    <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"></path>
                  </svg>
                </span>
              </summary>
              <div class="p-4 border-t border-gray-100">
                <p>Our teacher-to-child ratios exceed regulatory requirements to ensure quality care and individual attention. Ratios vary by age group: Infants (1:4), Toddlers (1:6), Preschool (1:8), and Kindergarten (1:10).</p>
              </div>
            </details>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>